                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160529-62-off341 t18160529-62-cd342"></join>, a watch, value 1l. 10s. two coats, value 2l. one pair of trowsers, value 15s. one waint coat, value 3s. one pair of boots, value 5s. and eight shillings in monies numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18160529-62-victim630" type="victimName">
